<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link1161659" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=1161659&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1964894-what-purpose-did-nirmal-s-diary-serve%2Fanswers%2F1161659-according-to-the-diary">flag</a>
</div>
